subsection.def:
Director
                    (處長) includes any Government surveyor
                appointed under subsection (1) of section 26 of the Ordinance;

paragraph.content:
all passenger ships engaged in the eastern trade area or the river trade
                    area which carry, or are certificated to carry, berthed or unberthed passengers;
                    and

subparagraph.content:
the delivery of air shall be at least 1
                        660 cubic feet per hour for each bed in a hospital;
                        and

paragraph.content:
provided with a wash-basin fitted with running fresh water and an efficient
                    and hygienic discharge system with waste pipes so arranged as to facilitate
                    cleaning;
